title: Ep 21: Nietzsche - Haters Gonna Hate
description: This episode covers the Madonna of the philosophy world - Frederich Nietzsche. He's popular, but often misunderstood and one of my absolute favorites. I cover the Genealogy of Morals and the idea of slave and master morality, the will to power and maybe a little ubermensch, too.
author: nadav@ymhstudios.com (Christina Pazsitzky)
